title: Second version of the Indian Super League gets to a colourful start this evening in Chennai
text: 3 Oct 2015The second version of the Indian Super League gets to a colourful start this evening at the Jawaharlal Nehru Stadium in Chennai.The first match of the season would be played between two of the favourite teams Chennaiyin FC and Atletico de Kolkata. Â»
